{
  "stem": "21482.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were lucky that she died because she was-- she was in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they started to call that there was an appellplatz, and everybody had to go out and march to the appellplatz, she died of a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, she saved herself so much, so much, because my youngest uncle was killed like the second day while we were in the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a painter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was painting the barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Amon Goth's standing yards, hundreds of yards away from him, just shot him for no reason.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No reason at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my grandfather was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And his two sons were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Shot him.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So she saved herself that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one of my cousins, a young cousin, I think he must have been maybe 18, maybe 20 at the time, he was killed by Amon Goth together with an uncle of his and a group of people that worked for Amon Goth in the camp.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was-- like he was the director of the Jewish police in the camp, the uncle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my cousin worked for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He gave him a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And those people, again, they were accused of trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were shot right in front of our eyes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My cousin was Moniek Ferber.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Such a nice, good-looking boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to-- we had to stand there and watch, walk around to see them dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to stand by while they were being burned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They burned them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to stand-- everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And especially the family, my aunt, mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we went to work for Oskar Schindler, it was like, you know, going to heaven, because we were away from Amon Goth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were away from all this killing.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
